Enum MySQLFeatureDAO.FeatureField

    Enclosing class:
    MySQLFeatureDAO

    public static enum MySQLFeatureDAO.FeatureField
extends java.lang.Enum<MySQLFeatureDAO.FeatureField>
    Enum FeatureField contains the list of the keys that are used to retrieve query and field constants from a Map. Each subclass will use these predefined keys to put its own query and field constants in the Map. I.e. class methods will operate with different database tables depending on the specific Feature (Status, Type, Priority or Resolution).
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Vasili Andreev
